name: Root Access (JaneYWei)
description:
You are a hacker.

You must build connections to nodes and download images to uncover the story of a young person and their grandma.

Note: The game is unfinished. If you get to picture 11 you've completed it.

=======================================

Controls:

left click - place piece/select button

right click - rotate piece

wasd / middle click drag / move mouse cursor to edge of playing field - scroll screen

======================================

Art: Ellen Hansen, Atticus McNaughton

Audio: Jane Wei

Programming: Tristan Lewis, Kiera Lord

Story: All of us

Design: Mostly Kiera Lord and Tristan Lewis, but all of us a little bit.
